12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 4668, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 4668. On July 1, 2001, there may be established a
16 branch of Northeastern State University within the Tulsa
17 metropolitan area City of Broken Arrow. The Oklahoma State Regents
18 for Higher Education are authorized to make lower division and upper
19 division undergraduate and graduate course offerings at the
20 Northeastern State University branch in Broken Arrow available as
21 the State Regents shall determine are appropriate. Undergraduate
22 degree programs offered through Oklahoma State University/Tulsa
23 shall not duplicate those undergraduate degree programs offered by
